Datomic,is,a,fully,transactional,cloud,ready,distributed,database,that,lets,you,build,flexible,distributed,systems,that,can,leverage,the,entire,history,of,your,critical,data,not,just,the,most,current,state,With,Datomic,you,can,build,databases,on,your,existing,infrastructure,or,jump,straight,to,the,cloud,The,Datomic,Client,API,is,a,library,for,interacting,with,Datomic